---
title: Buffalo Pork Belly & Onion Rings with Charred Corn Slaw & Cheesy Wedges
description: Does it get much better than melt-in-your-mouth pork belly with crispy, crunchy crackling? We didn’t think so, but with sides like these we’ve hit the jackpot! Golden onion rings, cheesy wedges and a refreshing charred corn slaw all come together alongside the pork for an epic feast of all things delicious.

